{"tid":783684,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★終於輪到中電！中電沽空大增，投資者須提高警覺。","createTime":"2018-08-17T17:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T00:22:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a58643686615dfbc2e2187fb0eedb4dfb2aa72a","tid":783684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"中電控股(00002)近兩個月升勢凌厲，自6月25日至今累逾17%，相比大市同期累跌6%，兩者走勢形成鮮明對比。不過，近日該股升勢似有放緩迹象，而且沽空大增，投資者須提高警覺。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，該股今日(17日)沽空金額及比率分別達1.18億元及32.4%，相較過去3日平均僅約為7,630萬及18.7%明顯增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/invtips/news_breaking_content.html?section=lit&amp;article_id=bkn-20180817174023957-0817_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Finvtips%2Fnews_breaking_content.html%3Fsection%3Dlit%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180817174023957-0817_00842_001&d=ZNJE44%2FX61GjFTrrixCz7AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=060aae85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/invtips/news_breaking_content.html?section=lit&amp;article_id=bkn-20180817174023957-0817_00842_001</a>"},{"pid":"3cfe58d60556e048cf871667693790f405ae3bc6","tid":783684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2dc68948cb83e46b746ea0b5613b0548a461d6","tid":783684,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:07:48.000Z","msg":"all stock need die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77a17a386cb41cf987ca61ac2b1648223887bcd","tid":783684,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q